ir, dead skin and urine.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pools\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"chemicals\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"especially chlorine\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"human debris\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"hair\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"dead skin\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"urine\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chlorine is used to prevent and kill algae, as well as protect swimmers from unhealthy compounds and waterborne illnesses,according to CNBC.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlorine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.570129342795396e-30, \"text\": \"Chlorine\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlorine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlorine\"}, {\"begin\": 1398, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999997937577731, \"rank\": 1.9620583448077533e-07, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"algae\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"unhealthy compounds\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"waterborne illnesses\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A balanced swimming pool has chlorine levels between 1.0 - 3.0 parts per million, according tothepoolpassion.com.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A balanced swimming pool\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"chlorine levels\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\"